query:
SELECT c.name as category_name, COUNT(*) as product_count 
FROM product_categories pc 
JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id 
WHERE c.id IN (11, 12, 13)
GROUP BY pc.categoryId, c.name 
ORDER BY c.id
